      • selfAmount

        public AccountEncryptedAmount.AccountEncryptedAmountBuilder selfAmount(EncryptedAmount selfAmount)
        Encrypted amount that is a result of this account's actions. In particular this list includes the aggregate of
        - remaining amounts that result when transferring to public balance
        - remaining amounts when transferring to another account
        - encrypted amounts that are transferred from public balance
        When a transfer is made all of these must always be used.
        Returns:
        this.

      • startIndex

        public AccountEncryptedAmount.AccountEncryptedAmountBuilder startIndex(EncryptedAmountIndex startIndex)
        Starting index for incoming encrypted amounts. If an aggregated amount is present then this index is associated with such an amount and the list of incoming encrypted amounts starts at the index `start_index + 1`.
        Returns:
        this.
